flavor_text_entries.gold:
If it flaps its
wings really fast,
it can generate shock waves that
will shatter win­
dows in the area.
flavor_text_entries.silver:
Its large eyes can
scan 360 degrees.
It looks in all directions to seek
out insects as its
prey.
flavor_text_entries.crystal:
It can see in all
directions without
moving its big eyes, helping it
spot attackers and
food right away.
flavor_text_entries.ruby:
YANMA is capable of seeing 360 degrees
without having to move its eyes.
It is a great flier that is adept at making sudden stops and turning midair.
This POKéMON uses its flying ability to
quickly chase down targeted prey.
